            <p class="technicalfielddefinition">
                <strong>KPI Options</strong> -  set the <i>Decoration</i> of the visualisation (<i>number</i> (default), <i>status</i>, <i>column</i> or <i>sparkline</i>). You can also set the meaning of the trending data (<i>Higher is better</i>&#160;(default) or <i>Lower is better</i>.) When <i>Decoration</i> is set to <i>Status</i>, the <i>Direction</i> setting will determine when a green arrow or red arrow will be displayed next to the values being returned by the query. </p>
